	* ChangeLog, build_w32.bat, w32/subproc/build.bat: 	* build_w32.bat (GCCBuild): Use "-gdwarf-2 -g3" instead of
		"-gstabs+ -ggdb3".  	* w32/subproc/build.bat (GCCBuild): Likewise.


2008-09-30  eliz <eliz>

	* ChangeLog, job.c: 	* job.c (construct_command_argv_internal): Avoid extra backslash
		in batch-mode Unixy shells.  Under DB_JOBS, display the contents
		of the batch file.

