	from the translations site so remove it.  The fdl.texi file was
	changed to not contain any @node entries, so add some around it in
	make.texi.

2007-07-16  R. Bernstein <rocky@gnu.org>

	* tests/run_make_tests.pl, tests/scripts/features/parallelism,
