	tests/ChangeLog, tests/test_driver.pl: Update GNU make to use
	Autoconf 2.53, Automake 1.6.1, Gettext 0.11.1. We're using Gettext's
	"external" feature to avoid including the intl code in the GNU make
	distribution.

