1995-03-10  roland <roland>

	* read.c: (find_char_unquote): Make second arg a string of stop chars instead
	of a single stop char.  Stop when any char in the string is hit. All
	callers changed. (find_semicolon): Pass stop chars "#;" to one
	find_char_unquote call, instead of using two calls.  If the match is
	not a ; but a #, return zero.

