	* remake.c: (update_file_1): When !MUST_MAKE, don't set FILE->update_status to
	zero before calling notice_finished_file. (notice_finished_file):
	Touch only when FILE->update_status is zero. (remake_file): Set
	FILE->update_status to zero after not calling execute_file_command
	and deciding to touch instead.

