	* GNUmakefile: (dist): Depend on rcs-mark first. (rcs-mark): New target.
	(rcs-mark-alpha, rcs-mark-beta): Use $(version-); append : to name
	for -N. (version-): New variable, removes dots (RCS doesn't like)
	from $(version).

